@startuml
title LangGraph RAG 时序图

actor User

participant "FastAPI\n(app/main.py)" as FastAPI
participant "API Router\n(routes.py)" as Router
participant "RAG Service\n(rag_service.py)" as Service
participant "LangGraph\n(rag_graph.py)" as Graph

participant "Retrieve Node\n(retrieve_node.py)" as Retrieve
participant "Embedding Model\n(embedding_model.py)" as Embedding
participant "Chroma VectorStore\n(chroma_store.py)" as Chroma
participant "Document Loader\n(document_loader.py)" as Loader
participant "Hybrid Retriever\n(hybrid_retriever.py)" as Hybrid

participant "Rerank Node\n(rerank_node.py)" as RerankNode
participant "CrossEncoder\n(reranker.py)" as Reranker

participant "Generate Node\n(generate_node.py)" as Generate
participant "LLM\n(Ollama / DeepSeek)" as LLM

database "Vector DB\n(data/vector_db)" as VectorDB
collections "Docs\n(data/docs)" as Docs

== 用户请求 ==

User -> FastAPI : POST /ask\n{query}
FastAPI -> Router : ask(request)

Router -> Service : ask_question(query)

== Service 调用 Graph ==

Service -> Graph : graph.invoke({query})

Graph -> Graph : 初始化 RAGState

note right of Graph
state = {
 query,
 docs,
 context,
 answer
}
end note

== 执行 retrieve_node ==

Graph -> Retrieve : retrieve_node(state)

Retrieve -> Embedding : get_embedding_model()

Embedding --> Retrieve : SentenceTransformerEmbeddings

Retrieve -> Chroma : load_vector_store(embedding)

Chroma -> VectorDB : 读取向量数据库
VectorDB --> Chroma : 返回DB实例
Chroma --> Retrieve : vector_db

Retrieve -> Loader : DirectoryLoader(data/docs)

Loader -> Docs : 读取原始文档
Docs --> Loader : docs
Loader --> Retrieve : docs

Retrieve -> Hybrid : create_hybrid_retriever(vector_db, docs)

note right of Hybrid
创建两个检索器
1 Vector Retriever
2 BM25 Retriever
组合为 EnsembleRetriever
end note

Hybrid --> Retrieve : hybrid_retriever

Retrieve -> Hybrid : get_relevant_documents(query)

Hybrid -> Chroma : 向量检索
Chroma -> VectorDB : similarity search
VectorDB --> Chroma : vector results
Chroma --> Hybrid : vector docs

Hybrid -> Hybrid : BM25 检索
Hybrid --> Retrieve : merged docs

Retrieve --> Graph : {docs}

== 执行 rerank_node ==

Graph -> RerankNode : rerank_node(state)

RerankNode -> Reranker : rerank(query, docs)

note right of Reranker
构建 pairs:
(query, doc)
end note

Reranker -> Reranker : CrossEncoder.predict()

Reranker --> RerankNode : ranked docs

RerankNode --> Graph : top5 docs

== 执行 generate_node ==

Graph -> Generate : generate_node(state)

Generate -> Generate : 构建 context\n拼接 docs

Generate -> LLM : 调用 LLM 生成答案

LLM --> Generate : answer

Generate --> Graph : {answer}

== 返回结果 ==

Graph --> Service : result

Service --> Router : answer

Router --> FastAPI : JSON response

FastAPI --> User : 返回答案

@enduml